dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Trempealeau_Zoning_2018.gdb'.
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.tremplocounty.com/tchome/landrecords/data.aspxThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
